overview: With a pulled muscle on her ass, Mia Malkova is seeking treatment for her pain. Armed with a bolster, Bree Daniels gives her all the relief she needs and more. Romi Rain is at the massage parlor again and can't help but notice how tight her masseuse's (Reena Sky) yoga pants are. They're so tight she can see her camel toe and can't help but get turned on. Once she's decided she wants her, there's nothing that's going to stop her from seducing Reena.
title: Return of the Bolster
